{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3adc750493","title":"毛泽东会见特立尼达和多巴哥总理威廉斯的谈话","origin":"根据文件的翻印件，翻印者未注明","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c3466168c5","index":0,"year":1974,"month":11,"day":6,"articleId":"3adc750493"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d731c14786","type":"title","text":"毛泽东会见特立尼达和多巴哥总理威廉斯的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3adc750493"},{"id":"50ec22e18f","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：噢！","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3adc750493"},{"id":"8cc24f1164","type":"paragraph","text":"历史这门学问是一门好学问。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3adc750493"},{"id":"79258cbd83","type":"paragraph","text":"威：我同意，我一直这样觉得。在我管理政府事务中，历史学总是给了我很大帮助。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3adc750493"},{"id":"60ce2f4ac5","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：譬如说，哥伦布发现新大陆。哥伦布是意大利人。他得了西班牙政府的同意，派他去了。路上遇到很大困难，几乎被人干掉了。在西班牙到加勒比的路上，船队很多人主张太危险啊，埋怨他。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3adc750493"},{"id":"934640aef9","type":"paragraph","text":"威：很对。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3adc750493"},{"id":"12a921be75","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：最后还是胜利了，VICTORY（胜利）。现在，最著名的一个意大利人是AMERIGO（亚美利哥）。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3adc750493"},{"id":"1e7ecc7421","type":"paragraph","text":"威：对，AMERIGO VESPUCCI（亚美利哥）。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3adc750493"},{"id":"6234f9007a","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：NORTH AMERICA（北美洲），LATIN AMERICA（拉丁美洲），都是以他的名字起名的。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3adc750493"},{"id":"878c5d55f2","type":"paragraph","text":"威：非常正确。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3adc750493"},{"id":"1695953473","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：古代商业意大利很发展。报纸，NEWSPAPER(报纸)首先在意大利出现。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3adc750493"},{"id":"cfa9f5dd9c","type":"paragraph","text":"威：是的。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3adc750493"},{"id":"e7465f864d","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：我是在PEKING UNIVERSITY(北京大学)上过新闻学。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3adc750493"},{"id":"0b5c8925c3","type":"paragraph","text":"威：那很好。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3adc750493"},{"id":"ef536a7b6f","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：我的先生对我这么讲。这位先生后来被军阀砍了。邵飘萍，他的名字也叫邵振青。鲁迅知道他。那个时候北京还坐马车，没有MOTORCAR（汽车）。1918年，ONE THOUSAND NINE HUNDRED AND EIGHTEEN(1918)。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3adc750493"},{"id":"d8d609ca71","type":"paragraph","text":"威：很久以前了！","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3adc750493"},{"id":"c070480509","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：是啊！我看见过第一次世界大战和和二次世界大战。现在到处讲和平，我看危险！第二次世界大战之后头几年，不讲和平，不要主要缓和紧张，而现在大讲特讲！没有病，就不要看医生。有病，他就要看医生。譬如我，就要看医生。现在地球害病，所以要讲缓和紧张，缓和国际紧张，要讲和平。现在给地球治病。我是持怀疑态度。国际会议，MEETING（会议，会见）这么多，美国这个国务卿到处跑（威点头，笑），相当怪!黄昏的时候，燕子忙，飞得低，雨要下了！","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3adc750493"}],"page":{"id":"ffe3147b1b","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3adc750493","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}